            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">How does the AI scanning work?</div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    Simply take a photo of your receipt, and our AI (powered by Google Gemini) automatically reads all
                    items, prices, tax, and tip. It's accurate and works with most receipt formats.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">How is tax and tip split?</div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    Tax and tip are split proportionally based on each person's share of the subtotal. This ensures
                    everyone pays their fair share, not just an equal split.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">Can I edit the tip amount?</div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    Yes! On the Summary screen, tap "Edit Tip" to adjust the tip amount. The totals will recalculate
                    automatically.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">What's included in Pro?</div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    Pro includes Annual Spending Reports (see your year in review), unlimited receipt history, and
                    priority AI processing for faster scans. It's $4.99/year.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">How do I cancel my subscription?</div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    Go to Settings ‚Üí Subscriptions in your iPhone settings, find SplitSmart, and tap Cancel
                    Subscription. You'll retain Pro access until the end of your billing period.
                </div>
